original: intros p0 p1 d0 d1 H1 H2. unfold prec_list_ref_ok in *. intros a H3. destruct H3 as [a' [H4 H5]]. specialize (H1 a'). specialize (H2 a'). specialize (H1 H4). specialize (H2 H5). destruct H1 as [s1 H6]. destruct H2 as [s2 H7]. exists s1. unfold preDTA_produit. rewrite H6, H7. reflexivity.
